      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1248507/" class="title-link">老钱这个人，这本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1248507"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mijianka/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1462713-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mijianka/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">米卡</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-11-27"
      class="main-meta">2007-11-27 23:55:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1248507_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      据说，钱理群先生颇喜“老钱”这一称谓，无论平辈还是晚生，皆可以“老钱”呼之。以我等晚生后辈来说，曰“老钱”而非“钱老”，的确拉近了心理距离，一种莫名的亲切感呼之欲出。     老钱的本行是中国现代文学研究，兼及二十世纪知识分子精神史。而老钱的影响绝不止于此。...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1248507/#comments">(9回应)</a>
